title: God of War II ps2 pal
description:
God of War II ps2 pal
=======================================================



god of war ii ps2 pal english

this is from a dvd9 (dual layer single sided dvd) so you'll need one of those to burn this image

i've burnt and played this and it works.

i personally used a verbatim dvd9, but there are others out there that also work.

don't forget to help seed for others who want this game as well!



-manny54321
